{"tid":857951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[易碎品] 韓國YG節目使用錯誤中國地圖 YG主席梁鉉錫公開道歉","createTime":"2018-10-11T12:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T23:02:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16590060e62aa4d0b983eb27685b7ca8518570c9","tid":857951,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"10月5日在韓國開播的YG自製節目《YG戰資》，被中國網友發現其中使用的中國地圖不完整，缺少部分領土。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/195/w630h365/20181011/BYbV-hkrzvkw5814742.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F195%2Fw630h365%2F20181011%2FBYbV-hkrzvkw5814742.png&h=f6c4453d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目中使用錯誤中地圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/185/w630h355/20181011/GETi-hkrzyan6882851.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F185%2Fw630h355%2F20181011%2FGETi-hkrzyan6882851.png&h=b5c99ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環節內容涉辱華<br />\n<br />\n新浪娛樂訊 近日，韓國新開播的YG自製節目《YG戰資》，被中國網友發現其中使用的中國地圖不完整，缺少部分領土。此外，節目中還有一個環節是讓韓國保鏢打扮成清朝人，並用中文說：&ldquo;我是豬。&rdquo;上述細節引發網友不滿。<br />\n<br />\n《YG戰資》是YG娛樂與Netflix聯合推出的全新情景網絡喜劇，該劇名稱是劇中&ldquo;YG戰略資料本部&rdquo;的縮寫。該劇由BigBang成員勝利主演，BLACKPINK、iKON、WINNER等YG所屬藝人也將出演。該劇的概念和陣容一經公佈，就引發了很多關注、。<br />\n<br />\n然而該劇播出之後，卻被中國網友發現其中使用的中國地圖不完整。劇中所使用的中國地圖，東南沿海地區均在地圖上缺失。此外，劇中還有讓兩個韓國保鏢打扮成清朝人的情節，兩個保鏢被抓後，還用中文說道：&ldquo;我是豬。&rdquo;上述細節引發很多中國網友不滿，質疑此舉涉嫌公然歧視中國人、破壞中國領土完整。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/yENY0XV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FyENY0XV.jpg&h=c3c9e253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月11日下午，YG娛樂會長梁鉉錫通過個人社交平台公開了道歉文。 &ldquo;向中國的各位粉絲鄭重地道歉。已經向相關負責人下達指令，盡快修改和刪除錯誤內容。今後將更加注意和小心。 &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n《YG戰資》被中國網友發現其中使用的中國地圖不完整，節目中所使用的中國地圖，多個地區均在地圖上缺失。此外，節目中還有讓兩個韓國保鏢打扮成清朝人的情節，兩個保鏢被抓後，還用中文說道：&ldquo;我是豬。&rdquo;上述細節引發很多中國網友不滿，質疑此舉涉嫌公然歧視中國人、破壞中國領土完整。<br />\n<br />\n今日在梁鉉錫個人SNS的最新一篇帖子中，中國網民們在不斷留言表示：&ldquo;YG這是在辱華&rdquo;、&ldquo;向中國道歉&rdquo;&ldquo;雖然喜歡YG歌手，但你不能隨意侮辱我的祖國&rdquo;等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png&h=2d0825c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77ed6a60438e56e12d2d0124f5963440d310d954","tid":857951,"uid":137732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"撚鳩完你扮道個歉又黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由你班生番繼續吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3cc6414b5e89bb413ef75214aa130ebbb9466b","tid":857951,"uid":52073,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/204715_dd560d7fc1a5cacfae73a75c2cfb8adf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F204715_dd560d7fc1a5cacfae73a75c2cfb8adf.png&h=a414ef47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af26621747c41216a78dc6b5b2c8c9ca059a4576","tid":857951,"uid":89931,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/221436_457764b89f89948f40fdfbcebbc36292.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F221436_457764b89f89948f40fdfbcebbc36292.jpeg&h=008d1007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正確道歉方法"},{"pid":"e61054b85f79c7813e9f7ec6d383d1d1840f129e","tid":857951,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"呢個節目咁多負面新聞出嘅，係咪冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}